rows.label: tev045301_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Thea about the Ganglion.

rows.label: tev045301_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Thea if anything is troubling her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Thea about the Ganglion.

rows.label: tev045301_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Thea about recent developments.

rows.label: tev045301_SEL1031
rows.name: Ask Thea about life in NLA.

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ganglion forged alliance with Cavern Clan.
They overran our home. Burned all to ash.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0002
rows.name:
They made servants of Cavern Clan and slaves of
Tree Clan in one blow![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0003
rows.name:
I hear they do this evil on many planets.
They threaten. Invade. Claim what they want.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0004
rows.name:
I cannot forgive such cowardice!
Had they not come to our planet,
Quegga would still be at my side.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0008
rows.name: Without my beloved, my spirit is lost.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0009
rows.name:
I have been nothing but burden to Hala.
This is shameful.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0010
rows.name:
I try to free myself from this gloom.
But I only sink deeper.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0011
rows.name: I miss Quegga. I want to be cradled in his arms again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0012
rows.name:
Ganglion forged alliance with Cavern Clan.
They overran our home. Burned all to ash.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0013
rows.name:
They made servants of Cavern Clan and slaves of
Tree Clan in one blow![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0014
rows.name:
I hear they do this evil on many planets.
They threaten. Invade. Claim what they want.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0015
rows.name:
But you are fighting back! Good. Continue this.
Such cowards must not be allowed to live.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0016
rows.name: Destroy them and avenge my Quegga![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0019
rows.name: Ah. There you are.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0020
rows.name: Thank you for helping me find strength to dance again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0021
rows.name:
When I wear these clothes, I feel different.
It is like my Quegga watches me dance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0022
rows.name:
My dancing also brings Hala joy.
It is good that I did not give it up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0023
rows.name: You can stay and watch me dance, if you like![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0024
rows.name:
I will do dance of great warrior.
Then Earth aliens will surely emerge victorious![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0030
rows.name:
I love this diner. Everyone treats me well.
Even though I am Prone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0031
rows.name:
In Ganglion captivity, they saw us as useless clods.
No better than slaves.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0032
rows.name:
I never thought I would do what I love in front of
crowd again. I have not felt this joy in so long![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0037
rows.name:
City is bursting with energy and excitement.
I wish Quegga could have seen it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0038
rows.name:
We promised to travel galaxy if we escaped Ganglion.
That way everyone could see me dance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045301_MSG0039
rows.name:
At least I dance for aliens here.
That way part of promise is fulfilled.[ST:wait ]
